pedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 743, \"end\": 746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dallas/Fort_Worth_International_Airport\", \"score\": 0.9997180147901555, \"rank\": 0.0002820647473105842, \"text\": \"DFW\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dallas/Fort_Worth_International_Airport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dallas/Fort_Worth_International_Airport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hong, 20, who trains in Houston, was born in Plano and is a sophomore at Stanford University.\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 801, \"end\": 808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"score\": 0.9988087411607482, \"rank\": 0.0005534088698965294, \"text\": \"Houston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\"}, {\"begin\": 822, \"end\": 827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Plano_Senior_High_School\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0899867578994815e-13, \"text\": \"Plano\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Plano_Senior_High_School\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Plano_Senior_High_School\"}, {\"begin\": 850, \"end\": 869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_Cardinal\", \"score\": 0.9999999946696789, \"rank\": 5.329903385574766e-09, \"text\": \"Stanford University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_Cardinal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_Cardinal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hong, who earned NCAA team and vault champion honors with Stanford, performed one of the hardest vaults in the world on Monday.\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 889, \"end\": 893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9980313710177985,